135 double calcAverage(vector<double> v_times)
136 {
137  double accum = 0;
138  for(double value : v_times)
139  {
140  accum += value;
141  }
142 
143  return accum / v_times.size();
144 }
145 
146 double calcDeviation(vector<double> v_times, double average)
147 {
148  double accum = 0;
149  for(double value : v_times)
150  {
151  accum += pow(value - average, 2);
152  }
153  return sqrt(accum / v_times.size());
154 }
155 
156 double calcAverage(vector<int> v_values)
157 {
158  double accum = 0;
159  int total = 0;
160  for(double value : v_values)
161  {
162  if(value == 0)
163  continue;
164  accum += value;
165  total++;
166  }
167 
168  return accum / total;
169 }
170 
171 double calcDeviation(vector<int> v_values, double average)
172 {
173  double accum = 0;
174  int total = 0;
175  for(double value : v_values)
176  {
177  if(value == 0)
178  continue;
179  accum += pow(value - average, 2);
180  total++;
181  }
182  return sqrt(accum / total);
183 }

1302 bool Tracking::ParseIMUParamFile(cv::FileStorage &fSettings)

1336 
1337 
1338

1340

1365  if(!node.empty() && node.isReal())
1366  {
1367  Na = node.real();
1368  }
1369  else
1370  {
1371  std::cerr << "*IMU.NoiseAcc parameter doesn't exist or is not a real number*" << std::endl;
1372  b_miss_params = true;
1373  }
1374 
1375  node = fSettings["IMU.GyroWalk"];
1376  if(!node.empty() && node.isReal())
1377  {
1378  Ngw = node.real();
1379  }
1380  else

1386  node = fSettings["IMU.AccWalk"];

1389  Naw = node.real();
1390  }
1391  else

1394  b_miss_params = true;

1397  node = fSettings["IMU.fastInit"];
1398  mFastInit = false;
1399  if(!node.empty())
1400  {
1401  mFastInit = static_cast<int>(fSettings["IMU.fastInit"]) != 0;

1405  cout << "Fast IMU initialization. Acceleration is not checked \n";
1406

1411

1751 void Tracking::PreintegrateIMU()
1752 {
1753 
1754  if(!mCurrentFrame.mpPrevFrame)
1755  {
1756  Verbose::PrintMess("non prev frame ", Verbose::VERBOSITY_NORMAL);
1757  mCurrentFrame.setIntegrated();
1758  return;
1759  }
1760 
1761  mvImuFromLastFrame.clear();
1762  mvImuFromLastFrame.reserve(mlQueueImuData.size());
1763  if(mlQueueImuData.size() == 0)
1764  {
1765  Verbose::PrintMess("Not IMU data in mlQueueImuData!!", Verbose::VERBOSITY_NORMAL);
1766  mCurrentFrame.setIntegrated();
1767  return;
1768  }
1769 
1770  while(true)
1771  {
1772  bool bSleep = false;
1773  {
1774  unique_lock<mutex> lock(mMutexImuQueue);
1775  if(!mlQueueImuData.empty())
1776  {
1777  IMU::Point* m = &mlQueueImuData.front();
1778  cout.precision(17);
1779  if(m->t<mCurrentFrame.mpPrevFrame->mTimeStamp-mImuPer)
1780  {
1781  mlQueueImuData.pop_front();
1782  }
1783  else if(m->t<mCurrentFrame.mTimeStamp-mImuPer)
1784  {
1785  mvImuFromLastFrame.push_back(*m);
1786  mlQueueImuData.pop_front();
1787  }
1788  else
1789  {
1790  mvImuFromLastFrame.push_back(*m);
1791  break;
1792  }
1793  }
1794  else
1795  {
1796  break;
1797  bSleep = true;
1798  }
1799  }
1800  if(bSleep)
1801  usleep(500);
1802  }
1803 
1804  const int n = mvImuFromLastFrame.size()-1;
1805  if(n==0){
1806  cout << "Empty IMU measurements vector!!!\n";
1807  return;
1808  }
1809 
1810  IMU::Preintegrated* pImuPreintegratedFromLastFrame = new IMU::Preintegrated(mLastFrame.mImuBias,mCurrentFrame.mImuCalib);
1811 
1812  for(int i=0; i<n; i++)
1813  {
1814  float tstep;
1815  Eigen::Vector3f acc, angVel;
1816  if((i==0) && (i<(n-1)))
1817  {
1818  float tab = mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].t-mvImuFromLastFrame[i].t;
1819  float tini = mvImuFromLastFrame[i].t-mCurrentFrame.mpPrevFrame->mTimeStamp;
1820  acc = (mvImuFromLastFrame[i].a+mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].a-
1821  (mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].a-mvImuFromLastFrame[i].a)*(tini/tab))*0.5f;
1822  angVel = (mvImuFromLastFrame[i].w+mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].w-
1823  (mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].w-mvImuFromLastFrame[i].w)*(tini/tab))*0.5f;
1824  tstep = mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].t-mCurrentFrame.mpPrevFrame->mTimeStamp;
1825  }
1826  else if(i<(n-1))
1827  {
1828  acc = (mvImuFromLastFrame[i].a+mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].a)*0.5f;
1829  angVel = (mvImuFromLastFrame[i].w+mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].w)*0.5f;
1830  tstep = mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].t-mvImuFromLastFrame[i].t;
1831  }
1832  else if((i>0) && (i==(n-1)))
1833  {
1834  float tab = mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].t-mvImuFromLastFrame[i].t;
1835  float tend = mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].t-mCurrentFrame.mTimeStamp;
1836  acc = (mvImuFromLastFrame[i].a+mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].a-
1837  (mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].a-mvImuFromLastFrame[i].a)*(tend/tab))*0.5f;
1838  angVel = (mvImuFromLastFrame[i].w+mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].w-
1839  (mvImuFromLastFrame[i+1].w-mvImuFromLastFrame[i].w)*(tend/tab))*0.5f;
1840  tstep = mCurrentFrame.mTimeStamp-mvImuFromLastFrame[i].t;
1841  }
1842  else if((i==0) && (i==(n-1)))
1843  {
1844  acc = mvImuFromLastFrame[i].a;
1845  angVel = mvImuFromLastFrame[i].w;
1846  tstep = mCurrentFrame.mTimeStamp-mCurrentFrame.mpPrevFrame->mTimeStamp;
1847  }
1848 
1849  if (!mpImuPreintegratedFromLastKF)
1850  cout << "mpImuPreintegratedFromLastKF does not exist" << endl;
1851  mpImuPreintegratedFromLastKF->IntegrateNewMeasurement(acc,angVel,tstep);
1852  pImuPreintegratedFromLastFrame->IntegrateNewMeasurement(acc,angVel,tstep);
1853  }
1854 
1855  mCurrentFrame.mpImuPreintegratedFrame = pImuPreintegratedFromLastFrame;
1856  mCurrentFrame.mpImuPreintegrated = mpImuPreintegratedFromLastKF;
1857  mCurrentFrame.mpLastKeyFrame = mpLastKeyFrame;
1858 
1859  mCurrentFrame.setIntegrated();
1860 
1861  //Verbose::PrintMess("Preintegration is finished!! ", Verbose::VERBOSITY_DEBUG);
1862 }

1865 bool Tracking::PredictStateIMU()
1866 {
1867  if(!mCurrentFrame.mpPrevFrame)
1868  {
1869  Verbose::PrintMess("No last frame", Verbose::VERBOSITY_NORMAL);
1870  return false;
1871  }
1872 
1873  if(mbMapUpdated && mpLastKeyFrame)
1874  {
1875  const Eigen::Vector3f twb1 = mpLastKeyFrame->GetImuPosition();
1876  const Eigen::Matrix3f Rwb1 = mpLastKeyFrame->GetImuRotation();
1877  const Eigen::Vector3f Vwb1 = mpLastKeyFrame->GetVelocity();
1878 
1879  const Eigen::Vector3f Gz(0, 0, -IMU::GRAVITY_VALUE);
1880  const float t12 = mpImuPreintegratedFromLastKF->dT;
1881 
1882  Eigen::Matrix3f Rwb2 = IMU::NormalizeRotation(Rwb1 * mpImuPreintegratedFromLastKF->GetDeltaRotation(mpLastKeyFrame->GetImuBias()));
1883  Eigen::Vector3f twb2 = twb1 + Vwb1*t12 + 0.5f*t12*t12*Gz+ Rwb1*mpImuPreintegratedFromLastKF->GetDeltaPosition(mpLastKeyFrame->GetImuBias());
1884  Eigen::Vector3f Vwb2 = Vwb1 + t12*Gz + Rwb1 * mpImuPreintegratedFromLastKF->GetDeltaVelocity(mpLastKeyFrame->GetImuBias());
1885  mCurrentFrame.SetImuPoseVelocity(Rwb2,twb2,Vwb2);
1886 
1887  mCurrentFrame.mImuBias = mpLastKeyFrame->GetImuBias();
1888  mCurrentFrame.mPredBias = mCurrentFrame.mImuBias;
1889  return true;
1890  }
1891  else if(!mbMapUpdated)
1892  {
1893  const Eigen::Vector3f twb1 = mLastFrame.GetImuPosition();
1894  const Eigen::Matrix3f Rwb1 = mLastFrame.GetImuRotation();
1895  const Eigen::Vector3f Vwb1 = mLastFrame.GetVelocity();
1896  const Eigen::Vector3f Gz(0, 0, -IMU::GRAVITY_VALUE);
1897  const float t12 = mCurrentFrame.mpImuPreintegratedFrame->dT;
1898 
1899  Eigen::Matrix3f Rwb2 = IMU::NormalizeRotation(Rwb1 * mCurrentFrame.mpImuPreintegratedFrame->GetDeltaRotation(mLastFrame.mImuBias));
1900  Eigen::Vector3f twb2 = twb1 + Vwb1*t12 + 0.5f*t12*t12*Gz+ Rwb1 * mCurrentFrame.mpImuPreintegratedFrame->GetDeltaPosition(mLastFrame.mImuBias);
1901  Eigen::Vector3f Vwb2 = Vwb1 + t12*Gz + Rwb1 * mCurrentFrame.mpImuPreintegratedFrame->GetDeltaVelocity(mLastFrame.mImuBias);
1902 
1903  mCurrentFrame.SetImuPoseVelocity(Rwb2,twb2,Vwb2);
1904 
1905  mCurrentFrame.mImuBias = mLastFrame.mImuBias;
1906  mCurrentFrame.mPredBias = mCurrentFrame.mImuBias;
1907  return true;
1908  }
1909  else
1910  cout << "not IMU prediction!!" << endl;
1911 
1912  return false;
1913 }

2849 bool Tracking::TrackReferenceKeyFrame()
2850 {
2851  // Compute Bag of Words vector
2852  mCurrentFrame.ComputeBoW();
2853 
2854  // We perform first an ORB matching with the reference keyframe
2855  // If enough matches are found we setup a PnP solver
2856  ORBmatcher matcher(0.7,true);
2857  vector<MapPoint*> vpMapPointMatches;
2858 
2859  int nmatches = matcher.SearchByBoW(mpReferenceKF,mCurrentFrame,vpMapPointMatches);
2860 
2861  if(nmatches<15)
2862  {
2863  cout << "TRACK_REF_KF: Less than 15 matches!!\n";
2864  return false;
2865  }
2866 
2867  mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints = vpMapPointMatches;
2868  mCurrentFrame.SetPose(mLastFrame.GetPose());
2869 
2870  //mCurrentFrame.PrintPointDistribution();
2871 
2872 
2873  // cout << " TrackReferenceKeyFrame mLastFrame.mTcw: " << mLastFrame.mTcw << endl;
2874  Optimizer::PoseOptimization(&mCurrentFrame);
2875 
2876  // Discard outliers
2877  int nmatchesMap = 0;
2878  for(int i =0; i<mCurrentFrame.N; i++)
2879  {
2880  //if(i >= mCurrentFrame.Nleft) break;
2881  if(mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints[i])
2882  {
2883  if(mCurrentFrame.mvbOutlier[i])
2884  {
2885  MapPoint* pMP = mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints[i];
2886 
2887  mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints[i]=static_cast<MapPoint*>(NULL);
2888  mCurrentFrame.mvbOutlier[i]=false;
2889  if(i < mCurrentFrame.Nleft){
2890  pMP->mbTrackInView = false;
2891  }
2892  else{
2893  pMP->mbTrackInViewR = false;
2894  }
2895  pMP->mbTrackInView = false;
2896  pMP->mnLastFrameSeen = mCurrentFrame.mnId;
2897  nmatches--;
2898  }
2899  else if(mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints[i]->Observations()>0)
2900  nmatchesMap++;
2901  }
2902  }
2903 
2904  if (mSensor == System::IMU_MONOCULAR || mSensor == System::IMU_STEREO || mSensor == System::IMU_RGBD)
2905  return true;
2906  else
2907  return nmatchesMap>=10;
2908 }

2910 void Tracking::UpdateLastFrame()
2911 {
2912  // Update pose according to reference keyframe
2913  KeyFrame* pRef = mLastFrame.mpReferenceKF;
2914  Sophus::SE3f Tlr = mlRelativeFramePoses.back();

3519  for(vector<MapPoint*>::iterator vit=mvpLocalMapPoints.begin(), vend=mvpLocalMapPoints.end(); vit!=vend; vit++)
3520  {
3521  MapPoint* pMP = *vit;
3522 
3523  if(pMP->mnLastFrameSeen == mCurrentFrame.mnId)
3524  continue;
3525  if(pMP->isBad())
3526  continue;
3527  // Project (this fills MapPoint variables for matching)
3528  if(mCurrentFrame.isInFrustum(pMP,0.5))
3529  {
3530  pMP->IncreaseVisible();
3531  nToMatch++;
3532  }
3533  if(pMP->mbTrackInView)
3534  {
3535  mCurrentFrame.mmProjectPoints[pMP->mnId] = cv::Point2f(pMP->mTrackProjX, pMP->mTrackProjY);
3536  }
3537  }
3538 
3539  if(nToMatch>0)
3540  {
3541  ORBmatcher matcher(0.8);
3542  int th = 1;
3543  if(mSensor==System::RGBD || mSensor==System::IMU_RGBD)
3544  th=3;
3545  if(mpAtlas->isImuInitialized())
3546  {
3547  if(mpAtlas->GetCurrentMap()->GetIniertialBA2())
3548  th=2;
3549  else
3550  th=6;
3551  }
3552  else if(!mpAtlas->isImuInitialized() && (mSensor==System::IMU_MONOCULAR || mSensor==System::IMU_STEREO || mSensor == System::IMU_RGBD))
3553  {
3554  th=10;
3555  }
3556 
3557  // If the camera has been relocalised recently, perform a coarser search
3558  if(mCurrentFrame.mnId<mnLastRelocFrameId+2)
3559  th=5;
3560 
3561  if(mState==LOST || mState==RECENTLY_LOST) // Lost for less than 1 second
3562  th=15; // 15
3563 
3564  int matches = matcher.SearchByProjection(mCurrentFrame, mvpLocalMapPoints, th, mpLocalMapper->mbFarPoints, mpLocalMapper->mThFarPoints);
3565  }

3760 bool Tracking::Relocalization()
3761 {
3762  Verbose::PrintMess("Starting relocalization", Verbose::VERBOSITY_NORMAL);
3763  // Compute Bag of Words Vector
3764  mCurrentFrame.ComputeBoW();
3765 
3766  // Relocalization is performed when tracking is lost
3767  // Track Lost: Query KeyFrame Database for keyframe candidates for relocalisation
3768  vector<KeyFrame*> vpCandidateKFs = mpKeyFrameDB->DetectRelocalizationCandidates(&mCurrentFrame, mpAtlas->GetCurrentMap());
3769 
3770  if(vpCandidateKFs.empty()) {
3771  Verbose::PrintMess("There are not candidates", Verbose::VERBOSITY_NORMAL);
3772  return false;
3773  }
3774 
3775  const int nKFs = vpCandidateKFs.size();
3776 
3777  // We perform first an ORB matching with each candidate
3778  // If enough matches are found we setup a PnP solver
3779  ORBmatcher matcher(0.75,true);
3780 
3781  vector<MLPnPsolver*> vpMLPnPsolvers;
3782  vpMLPnPsolvers.resize(nKFs);
3783 
3784  vector<vector<MapPoint*> > vvpMapPointMatches;
3785  vvpMapPointMatches.resize(nKFs);
3786 
3787  vector<bool> vbDiscarded;
3788  vbDiscarded.resize(nKFs);
3789 
3790  int nCandidates=0;
3791 
3792  for(int i=0; i<nKFs; i++)
3793  {
3794  KeyFrame* pKF = vpCandidateKFs[i];
3795  if(pKF->isBad())
3796  vbDiscarded[i] = true;
3797  else
3798  {
3799  int nmatches = matcher.SearchByBoW(pKF,mCurrentFrame,vvpMapPointMatches[i]);
3800  if(nmatches<15)
3801  {
3802  vbDiscarded[i] = true;
3803  continue;
3804  }
3805  else
3806  {
3807  MLPnPsolver* pSolver = new MLPnPsolver(mCurrentFrame,vvpMapPointMatches[i]);
3808  pSolver->SetRansacParameters(0.99,10,300,6,0.5,5.991); //This solver needs at least 6 points
3809  vpMLPnPsolvers[i] = pSolver;
3810  nCandidates++;
3811  }
3812  }
3813  }
3814 
3815  // Alternatively perform some iterations of P4P RANSAC
3816  // Until we found a camera pose supported by enough inliers
3817  bool bMatch = false;
3818  ORBmatcher matcher2(0.9,true);
3819 
3820  while(nCandidates>0 && !bMatch)
3821  {
3822  for(int i=0; i<nKFs; i++)
3823  {
3824  if(vbDiscarded[i])
3825  continue;
3826 
3827  // Perform 5 Ransac Iterations
3828  vector<bool> vbInliers;
3829  int nInliers;
3830  bool bNoMore;
3831 
3832  MLPnPsolver* pSolver = vpMLPnPsolvers[i];
3833  Eigen::Matrix4f eigTcw;
3834  bool bTcw = pSolver->iterate(5,bNoMore,vbInliers,nInliers, eigTcw);
3835 
3836  // If Ransac reachs max. iterations discard keyframe
3837  if(bNoMore)
3838  {
3839  vbDiscarded[i]=true;
3840  nCandidates--;
3841  }
3842 
3843  // If a Camera Pose is computed, optimize
3844  if(bTcw)
3845  {
3846  Sophus::SE3f Tcw(eigTcw);
3847  mCurrentFrame.SetPose(Tcw);
3848  // Tcw.copyTo(mCurrentFrame.mTcw);
3849 
3850  set<MapPoint*> sFound;
3851 
3852  const int np = vbInliers.size();
3853 
3854  for(int j=0; j<np; j++)
3855  {
3856  if(vbInliers[j])
3857  {
3858  mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints[j]=vvpMapPointMatches[i][j];
3859  sFound.insert(vvpMapPointMatches[i][j]);
3860  }
3861  else
3862  mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints[j]=NULL;
3863  }
3864 
3865  int nGood = Optimizer::PoseOptimization(&mCurrentFrame);
3866 
3867  if(nGood<10)
3868  continue;
3869 
3870  for(int io =0; io<mCurrentFrame.N; io++)
3871  if(mCurrentFrame.mvbOutlier[io])
3872  mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints[io]=static_cast<MapPoint*>(NULL);
3873 
3874  // If few inliers, search by projection in a coarse window and optimize again
3875  if(nGood<50)
3876  {
3877  int nadditional =matcher2.SearchByProjection(mCurrentFrame,vpCandidateKFs[i],sFound,10,100);
3878 
3879  if(nadditional+nGood>=50)
3880  {
3881  nGood = Optimizer::PoseOptimization(&mCurrentFrame);
3882 
3883  // If many inliers but still not enough, search by projection again in a narrower window
3884  // the camera has been already optimized with many points
3885  if(nGood>30 && nGood<50)
3886  {
3887  sFound.clear();
3888  for(int ip =0; ip<mCurrentFrame.N; ip++)
3889  if(mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints[ip])
3890  sFound.insert(mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints[ip]);
3891  nadditional =matcher2.SearchByProjection(mCurrentFrame,vpCandidateKFs[i],sFound,3,64);
3892 
3893  // Final optimization
3894  if(nGood+nadditional>=50)
3895  {
3896  nGood = Optimizer::PoseOptimization(&mCurrentFrame);
3897 
3898  for(int io =0; io<mCurrentFrame.N; io++)
3899  if(mCurrentFrame.mvbOutlier[io])
3900  mCurrentFrame.mvpMapPoints[io]=NULL;
3901  }
3902  }
3903  }
3904  }
3905 
3906 
3907  // If the pose is supported by enough inliers stop ransacs and continue
3908  if(nGood>=50)
3909  {
3910  bMatch = true;
3911  break;
3912  }
3913  }
3914  }
3915  }
3916 
3917  if(!bMatch)
3918  {
3919  return false;
3920  }
3921  else
3922  {
3923  mnLastRelocFrameId = mCurrentFrame.mnId;
3924  cout << "Relocalized!!" << endl;
3925  return true;
3926  }
